data.description: This updated 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home in the far N.E. has hardwood, tile and carpet floors throughout, a beautiful kitchen, separate dining room, a large spacious living room, a sliding glass door to a large deck, a fenced-in backyard . The home has central A/C & heat. The finished basement has a Family Room, laundry room, a bonus room, a half bath and lots of storage 2019-Entire house painted, carpet installed on steps and in hallway AND 5-6 foot vinyl fence installed.  2021-Roof sealed. (1 year left on warranty) Master bedroom and powder room updated. Master bedroom closet barn doors installed. Vinyl plank flooring installed in kitchen, dining room and foyer.  2022-electric upgraded. Brand new heater/ac unit.  2023-Brand new windows, patio/deck doors AND vinyl plank flooring (basement) installed. All planks replaced on deck and entire home power washed and repainted outside.
